<span begin="6.920" end="7.090">を</span><span begin="7.150" end="7.280">見</span><span begin="7.400" end="7.590">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">梦见漂浮在人工的天空中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">인공 하늘에 떠오르는 꿈을 꾸었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I dreamed of it floating in an artificial sky</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jinkou no sora de ukabu yume o mita</span></p><p begin="8.070" end="11.780" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="8.070" end="8.440">動</span><span begin="8.520" end="8.730">か</span><span begin="8.750" end="8.970">な</span><span begin="8.970" end="9.090">い</span><span begin="9.140" end="9.540">水</span><span begin="9.620" end="9.970">平</span><span begin="10.020" end="10.520">線</span><span begin="10.520" end="10.670">の</span><span begin="10.740" end="10.850">向</span><span begin="10.960" end="11.190">こ</span><span begin="11.190" end="11.380">う</span><span begin="11.410" end="11.590">で</span><span begin="11.640" end="11.780">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">即使在静止的地平线彼端</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">움직이지 않는 수평선 너머에서도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even beyond the motionless horizon</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ugokanai suiheisen no mukou demo</span></p><p begin="11.810" end="14.400" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="11.810" end="11.990">夜</span><span begin="12.030" end="12.480">空</span><span begin="12.510" end="12.640">は</span><span begin="12.740" end="12.940">泣</span><span begin="12.940" end="13.050">い</span><span begin="13.180" end="13.370">て</span><span begin="13.400" end="13.510">る</span><span begin="13.630" end="13.750">と</span><span begin="13.840" end="14.020">良</span><span begin="14.020" end="14.180">い</span><span begin="14.280" end="14.400">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">夜空若是在哭泣就好了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">밤하늘은 울고 있었으면 좋겠네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I hope the night sky is crying</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yozora wa naiteru to ii na</span></p><p begin="29.320" end="32.160" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.320" end="29.520">思</span><span begin="29.580" end="29.970">春</span><span begin="30.030" end="30.250">期</span><span begin="30.290" end="30.440">の</span><span begin="30.530" end="30.840">代</span><span begin="30.920" end="31.360">償</span><span begin="31.400" end="31.500">で</span><span begin="31.550" end="31.640">し</span><span begin="31.640" end="31.840">ょ</span><span begin="31.840" end="31.970">う</span><span begin="32.040" end="32.160">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是青春期的代价吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사춘기의 대가일까요</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is this the price of adolescence</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shishunki no daishou deshou ka</span></p><p begin="32.240" end="33.960" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="32.240" end="32.540">錯</span><span begin="32.720" end="33.140">覚</span><span begin="33.160" end="33.260">で</span><span begin="33.290" end="33.410">し</span><span begin="33.410" end="33.640">ょ</span><span begin="33.640" end="33.770">う</span><span begin="33.840" end="33.960">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是错觉吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">착각일까요</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is it an illusion</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sakkaku deshou ka</span></p><p begin="34.060" end="36.070" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="34.060" end="34.480">教</span><span begin="34.520" end="34.910">育</span><span begin="34.960" end="35.120">な</span><span begin="35.190" end="35.360">の</span><span begin="35.410" end="35.550">で</span><span begin="35.610" end="35.750">す</span><span begin="35.850" end="36.070">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是教育的结果吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">교육인 건가요</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is it education</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kyouiku na no desu ka</span></p><p begin="36.490" end="39.940" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.490" end="36.880">神</span><span begin="36.940" end="37.330">頼</span><span begin="37.380" end="37.500">み</span><span begin="37.560" end="38.010">寸</span><span begin="38.040" end="38.480">前</span><span begin="38.510" end="38.640">で</span> <span begin="38.690" end="38.950">す</span><span begin="38.950" end="39.080">れ</span><span begin="39.160" end="39.620">違</span><span begin="39.620" end="39.810">っ</span><span begin="39.810" end="39.940">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在求神拜佛的前一刻 擦肩而过</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">신에게 빌기 직전 엇갈렸어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Just on the verge of praying to God we passed each other</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kamidanomi sunzen de surechigatta</span></p><p begin="40.040" end="41.060" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.040" end="40.400">快</span><span begin="40.450" end="40.920">速</span><span begin="40.940" end="41.060">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">飞速地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">쾌속으로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">On the rapid train</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kaisoku de</span></p><p begin="41.160" end="42.950" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="41.160" end="41.600">現</span><span begin="41.620" end="42.050">実</span><span begin="42.080" end="42.200">に</span><span begin="42.270" end="42.720">帰</span><span begin="42.740" end="42.950">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">回归现实</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">현실로 돌아가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Returning to reality</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Genjitsu ni kaeru</span></p><p begin="45.150" end="46.760" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="45.150" end="45.270">き</span><span begin="45.390" end="45.580">み</span><span begin="45.620" end="45.730">の</span><span begin="45.780" end="46.050">せ</span><span begin="46.050" end="46.230">い</span><span begin="46.280" end="46.480">だ</span><span begin="46.510" end="46.760">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">都是你的错哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네 탓이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s your fault</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi no sei da yo</span></p><p begin="48.710" end="53.380" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="48.710" end="48.890">き</span><span begin="48.970" end="49.130">み</span><span begin="49.160" end="49.300">の</span><span begin="49.360" end="49.630">せ</span><span begin="49.630" end="49.800">い</span><span begin="49.850" end="50.030">だ</span><span begin="50.070" end="53.380">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">都是你的错哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네 탓이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s your fault</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi no sei da yo</span></p><p begin="53.590" end="55.280" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="53.590" end="53.990">性</span><span begin="54.080" end="54.480">格</span><span begin="54.510" end="54.620">で</span><span begin="54.660" end="54.740">し</span><span begin="54.740" end="54.960">ょ</span><span begin="54.960" end="55.080">う</span><span begin="55.150" end="55.280">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是性格使然吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">성격일까요</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is it my personality</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Seikaku deshou ka</span></p><p begin="55.350" end="57.190" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="55.350" end="55.700">錯</span><span begin="55.840" end="56.290">覚</span><span begin="56.290" end="56.400">で</span><span begin="56.440" end="56.530">し</span><span begin="56.530" end="56.750">ょ</span><span begin="56.750" end="56.930">う</span><span begin="56.970" end="57.190">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是错觉吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">착각일까요</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is it an illusion</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sakkaku deshou ka</span></p><p begin="56.700" end="1:00.890" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="56.700" end="56.920">き</span><span begin="56.970" end="57.160">み</span><span begin="57.160" end="57.350">を</span> <span begin="57.410" end="57.750">ど</span><span begin="57.750" end="57.860">ん</span><span begin="57.860" end="58.190">ど</span><span begin="58.190" end="58.240">ん</span><span begin="58.240" end="58.440">好</span><span begin="58.510" end="58.720">き</span><span begin="58.750" end="58.940">に</span><span begin="58.970" end="59.200">な</span><span begin="59.200" end="59.400">っ</span><span begin="59.400" end="59.600">て</span><span begin="59.830" end="1:00.190">ゆ</span><span begin="1:00.290" end="1:00.450">く</span><span begin="1:00.510" end="1:00.700">の</span><span begin="1:00.740" end="1:00.890">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">变得越来越喜欢你这件事</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너를 점점 좋아하게 되는 게</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Falling more and more in love with you</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi o dondon suki ni natte yuku no ga</span></p><p begin="1:00.950" end="1:03.580" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:00.950" end="1:01.300">だ</span><span begin="1:01.300" end="1:01.400">ん</span><span begin="1:01.400" end="1:01.730">だ</span><span begin="1:01.730" end="1:01.870">ん</span><span begin="1:01.870" end="1:02.220">怖</span><span begin="1:02.330" end="1:02.450">く</span><span begin="1:02.520" end="1:03.210">な</span><span begin="1:03.210" end="1:03.420">っ</span><span begin="1:03.420" end="1:03.580">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">渐渐变得让人害怕</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">갈수록 무서워져서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is gradually becoming terrifying</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dandan kowaku natte</span></p><p begin="1:03.820" end="1:08.510" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:03.820" end="1:04.270">遊</span><span begin="1:04.290" end="1:04.440">び</span><span begin="1:04.490" end="1:04.820">足</span><span begin="1:04.820" end="1:04.940">り</span><span begin="1:04.970" end="1:05.320">な</span><span begin="1:05.320" end="1:05.390">い</span><span begin="1:05.390" end="1:05.420">、</span><span begin="1:05.420" end="1:05.590">埋</span><span begin="1:05.640" end="1:05.830">ま</span><span begin="1:05.860" end="1:06.030">ら</span><span begin="1:06.070" end="1:06.360">な</span><span begin="1:06.360" end="1:06.460">い</span><span begin="1:06.500" end="1:06.780">な</span><span begin="1:06.780" end="1:06.950">ん</span><span begin="1:06.950" end="1:07.330">て</span><span begin="1:07.400" end="1:07.810">言</span><span begin="1:07.850" end="1:08.010">葉</span><span begin="1:08.070" end="1:08.510">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">还没玩够 无法填补这样的话语</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">덜 놀았어, 채워지지 않아 같은 말은</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Words like not playing enough or feeling unfulfilled</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Asobitarinai, umaranai nante kotoba wa</span></p><p begin="1:08.950" end="1:10.430" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:08.950" end="1:09.170">言</span><span begin="1:09.170" end="1:09.320">え</span><span begin="1:09.420" end="1:09.640">な</span><span begin="1:09.640" end="1:10.430">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无法说出口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">할 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I cannot say</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ienai</span></p><p begin="1:10.900" end="1:15.120" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:10.900" end="1:11.110">き</span><span begin="1:11.170" end="1:11.350">み</span><span begin="1:11.390" end="1:11.520">が</span> <span begin="1:11.580" end="1:11.830">す</span><span begin="1:11.830" end="1:12.040">っ</span><span begin="1:12.040" end="1:12.200">と</span><span begin="1:12.280" end="1:12.500">綺</span><span begin="1:12.500" end="1:12.910">麗</span><span begin="1:12.970" end="1:13.150">に</span><span begin="1:13.190" end="1:13.400">な</span><span begin="1:13.400" end="1:13.630">っ</span><span begin="1:13.630" end="1:13.830">て</span><span begin="1:14.080" end="1:14.430">ゆ</span><span begin="1:14.530" end="1:14.690">く</span><span begin="1:14.750" end="1:14.920">の</span><span begin="1:14.980" end="1:15.120">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你瞬间变得越来越漂亮这件事</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 훌쩍 예뻐져 가는 게</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Seeing you quickly become so beautiful</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi ga sutto kirei ni natte yuku no ga</span></p><p begin="1:15.190" end="1:17.810" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:15.190" end="1:15.470">だ</span><span begin="1:15.470" end="1:15.620">ん</span><span begin="1:15.620" end="1:15.890">だ</span><span begin="1:15.890" end="1:16.040">ん</span><span begin="1:16.040" end="1:16.510">嫌</span><span begin="1:16.510" end="1:16.680">に</span><span begin="1:16.720" end="1:17.460">な</span><span begin="1:17.460" end="1:17.620">っ</span><span begin="1:17.620" end="1:17.810">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">渐渐变得让人讨厌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">갈수록 싫어져서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is gradually becoming hateful</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dandan iya ni natte</span></p><p begin="1:18.070" end="1:22.770" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:18.070" end="1:18.460">嘘</span><span begin="1:18.520" end="1:18.660">み</span><span begin="1:18.740" end="1:19.060">た</span><span begin="1:19.060" end="1:19.160">い</span><span begin="1:19.200" end="1:19.300">な</span><span begin="1:19.360" end="1:19.800">空</span><span begin="1:19.840" end="1:20.020">に</span> <span begin="1:20.060" end="1:20.100">ぎ</span><span begin="1:20.100" end="1:20.240">ゅ</span><span begin="1:20.300" end="1:20.330">ぎ</span><span begin="1:20.330" end="1:20.560">ゅ</span><span begin="1:20.560" end="1:20.720">っ</span><span begin="1:20.720" end="1:20.890">と</span><span begin="1:21.180" end="1:21.570">噛</span><span begin="1:21.630" end="1:21.740">み</span><span begin="1:21.820" end="1:22.060">付</span><span begin="1:22.060" end="1:22.190">い</span><span begin="1:22.280" end="1:22.770">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">对着那如谎言般的天空 狠狠地咬下去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">거짓말 같은 하늘을 꽉 깨물고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Biting down hard on the lie-like sky</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Uso mitai na sora ni gyugyutto kamitsuite</span></p><p begin="1:23.150" end="1:25.630" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:23.150" end="1:23.550">弾</span><span begin="1:23.620" end="1:23.770">け</span><span begin="1:23.850" end="1:25.630">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">破裂了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">터졌어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It burst</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hajiketa</span></p><p begin="1:30.880" end="1:32.800" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:30.880" end="1:31.290">性</span><span begin="1:31.400" end="1:31.820">格</span><span begin="1:31.850" end="1:31.960">で</span><span begin="1:32.010" end="1:32.080">し</span><span begin="1:32.080" end="1:32.300">ょ</span><span begin="1:32.300" end="1:32.430">う</span><span begin="1:32.510" end="1:32.800">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是性格使然吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">성격일까요</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is it my personality</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Seikaku deshou ka</span></p><p begin="1:36.230" end="1:37.920" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:36.230" end="1:36.650">性</span><span begin="1:36.760" end="1:37.130">格</span><span begin="1:37.160" end="1:37.290">で</span><span begin="1:37.330" end="1:37.410">し</span><span begin="1:37.410" end="1:37.630">ょ</span><span begin="1:37.630" end="1:37.760">う</span><span begin="1:37.830" end="1:37.920">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是性格使然吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">성격일까요</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is it my personality</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Seikaku deshou ka</span></p><p begin="1:38.020" end="1:39.870" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:38.020" end="1:38.330">錯</span><span begin="1:38.510" end="1:38.930">覚</span><span begin="1:38.960" end="1:39.070">で</span><span begin="1:39.120" end="1:39.190">し</span><span begin="1:39.190" end="1:39.370">ょ</span><span begin="1:39.370" end="1:39.540">う</span><span begin="1:39.630" end="1:39.870">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是错觉吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">착각일까요</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is it an illusion</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sakkaku deshou ka</span></p><p begin="1:47.580" end="1:51.410" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:47.580" end="1:47.990">少</span><span begin="1:48.040" end="1:48.250">し</span><span begin="1:48.280" end="1:48.410">だ</span><span begin="1:48.490" end="1:48.670">け</span><span begin="1:48.700" end="1:48.870">夜</span><span begin="1:48.940" end="1:49.370">風</span><span begin="1:49.390" end="1:49.530">が</span><span begin="1:49.610" end="1:49.950">恋</span><span begin="1:50.010" end="1:50.190">し</span><span begin="1:50.260" end="1:50.430">く</span><span begin="1:50.510" end="1:51.410">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">稍微有些贪恋夜晚的微风</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">밤바람이 조금 그리워서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Missing the night breeze just a little</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sukoshi dake yokaze ga koishikute</span></p><p begin="1:54.700" end="2:00.080" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:54.700" end="1:54.890">お</span><span begin="1:54.890" end="1:55.130">お</span><span begin="1:55.180" end="1:55.300">げ</span><span begin="1:55.340" end="1:55.550">さ</span><span begin="1:55.610" end="1:55.880">に</span><span begin="1:55.880" end="1:56.510">息</span><span begin="1:56.510" end="1:56.640">を</span><span begin="1:56.690" end="1:56.970">吸</span><span begin="1:56.970" end="1:57.110">い</span><span begin="1:57.180" end="1:57.420">込</span><span begin="1:57.420" end="1:57.620">ん</span><span begin="1:57.620" end="1:58.950">で</span><span begin="1:59.400" end="1:59.680">み</span><span begin="1:59.830" end="2:00.080">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试着夸张地深吸了一口气</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">과장되게 숨을 들이마셔 보았어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I tried taking an exaggeratedly deep breath</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Oogesa ni iki o suikonde mita</span></p><p begin="2:00.700" end="2:04.470" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.700" end="2:00.940">振</span><span begin="2:00.960" end="2:01.130">り</span><span begin="2:01.180" end="2:01.320">向</span><span begin="2:01.390" end="2:01.620">け</span><span begin="2:01.820" end="2:02.060">ば</span> <span begin="2:02.250" end="2:02.380">そ</span><span begin="2:02.510" end="2:02.650">こ</span><span begin="2:02.700" end="2:02.880">は</span><span begin="2:02.950" end="2:03.390">天</span><span begin="2:03.390" end="2:03.750">国</span><span begin="2:03.820" end="2:04.140">で</span><span begin="2:04.160" end="2:04.230">す</span><span begin="2:04.280" end="2:04.470">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">若是回首 那里会是天堂吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">뒤돌아보면 그곳은 천국인가요</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If I turn around is it heaven there</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Furimukeba soko wa tengoku desu ka</span></p><p begin="2:04.470" end="2:05.750" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:04.470" end="2:04.710">い</span><span begin="2:04.710" end="2:04.940">や</span> <span begin="2:05.190" end="2:05.420">や</span> <span begin="2:05.600" end="2:05.750">や</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不 呀 呀</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아니 니 니</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">No no no</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Iya ya ya</span></p><p begin="2:05.810" end="2:09.150" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:05.810" end="2:05.990">こ</span><span begin="2:06.070" end="2:06.220">こ</span><span begin="2:06.270" end="2:06.440">よ</span><span begin="2:06.520" end="2:06.890">り</span><span begin="2:06.950" end="2:07.100">も</span><span begin="2:07.160" end="2:07.340">ひ</span><span begin="2:07.390" end="2:07.630">ど</span><span begin="2:07.630" end="2:07.790">い</span><span begin="2:07.840" end="2:07.990">ば</span><span begin="2:08.020" end="2:08.070">し</span><span begin="2:08.070" end="2:08.260">ょ</span><span begin="2:08.280" end="2:08.430">で</span><span begin="2:08.470" end="2:08.710">す</span><span begin="2:08.950" end="2:09.150">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是比这里还要糟糕的地方吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">여기보다 끔찍한 곳인가요</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is it a place worse than here</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koko yori mo hidoi basho desu ka</span></p><p begin="2:09.360" end="2:10.740" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:09.360" end="2:09.600">聞</span><span begin="2:09.600" end="2:09.760">い</span><span begin="2:09.830" end="2:10.000">て</span><span begin="2:10.070" end="2:10.340">な</span><span begin="2:10.340" end="2:10.440">い</span><span begin="2:10.500" end="2:10.740">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你没在听吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">안 듣고 있나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">You&apos;re not listening huh</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kiitenai ka</span></p><p begin="2:10.950" end="2:11.580" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:10.950" end="2:11.240">だ</span><span begin="2:11.240" end="2:11.410">っ</span><span begin="2:11.410" end="2:11.580">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">毕竟</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Datte</span></p><p begin="2:11.830" end="2:13.530" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:11.830" end="2:12.110">特</span><span begin="2:12.290" end="2:12.680">別</span><span begin="2:12.700" end="2:12.870">だ</span><span begin="2:12.930" end="2:13.190">も</span><span begin="2:13.190" end="2:13.380">ん</span><span begin="2:13.380" end="2:13.530">ね</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是特别的嘛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">특별하니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s special isn&apos;t it</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tokubetsu da mon ne</span></p><p begin="2:13.630" end="2:15.440" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:13.630" end="2:13.930">特</span><span begin="2:14.060" end="2:14.490">別</span><span begin="2:14.510" end="2:14.670">だ</span><span begin="2:14.730" end="2:14.960">も</span><span begin="2:14.960" end="2:15.170">ん</span><span begin="2:15.170" end="2:15.440">ね</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是特别的嘛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">특별하니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s special isn&apos;t it</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tokubetsu da mon ne</span></p><p begin="2:22.500" end="2:27.330" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:22.500" end="2:22.930">完</span><span begin="2:22.960" end="2:23.410">全</span><span begin="2:23.410" end="2:23.560">な</span><span begin="2:23.590" end="2:24.020">空</span><span begin="2:24.070" end="2:27.330">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">完美的天空</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">완전한 하늘은</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The perfect sky is</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kanzen na sora wa</span></p><p begin="2:27.810" end="2:29.550" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:27.810" end="2:28.280">完</span><span begin="2:28.300" end="2:28.730">全</span><span begin="2:28.730" end="2:28.860">な</span><span begin="2:28.920" end="2:29.350">空</span><span begin="2:29.380" end="2:29.550">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">完美的天空</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">완전한 하늘은</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The perfect sky is</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kanzen na sora wa</span></p><p begin="2:29.620" end="2:32.640" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:29.620" end="2:29.940">特</span><span begin="2:30.050" end="2:30.490">別</span><span begin="2:30.520" end="2:30.690">だ</span><span begin="2:30.740" end="2:30.920">も</span><span begin="2:30.920" end="2:31.140">ん</span><span begin="2:31.190" end="2:32.640">ね</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是特别的嘛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">특별하니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Special isn&apos;t it</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tokubetsu da mon ne</span></p><p begin="2:30.910" end="2:35.120" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:30.910" end="2:31.140">き</span><span begin="2:31.180" end="2:31.380">み</span><span begin="2:31.380" end="2:31.580">を</span> <span begin="2:31.620" end="2:31.990">ど</span><span begin="2:31.990" end="2:32.090">ん</span><span begin="2:32.090" end="2:32.430">ど</span><span begin="2:32.430" end="2:32.480">ん</span><span begin="2:32.480" end="2:32.640">好</span><span begin="2:32.730" end="2:32.920">き</span><span begin="2:32.950" end="2:33.150">に</span><span begin="2:33.190" end="2:33.420">な</span><span begin="2:33.420" end="2:33.640">っ</span><span begin="2:33.640" end="2:33.850">て</span><span begin="2:34.070" end="2:34.410">ゆ</span><span begin="2:34.480" end="2:34.600">く</span><span begin="2:34.700" end="2:34.930">か</span><span begin="2:34.960" end="2:35.120">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为变得越来越喜欢你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너를 점점 좋아하게 되니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because I am falling more and more in love with you</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi o dondon suki ni natte yuku kara</span></p><p begin="2:35.170" end="2:37.810" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:35.170" end="2:35.560">断</span><span begin="2:35.590" end="2:35.970">然</span> <span begin="2:36.030" end="2:36.430">弱</span><span begin="2:36.530" end="2:36.700">く</span><span begin="2:36.740" end="2:37.410">な</span><span begin="2:37.410" end="2:37.640">っ</span><span begin="2:37.640" end="2:37.810">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">变得无比软弱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">단연코 약해졌어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I have become absolutely weaker</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Danzen yowaku natta</span></p><p begin="2:38.080" end="2:41.360" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:38.080" end="2:38.210">わ</span><span begin="2:38.290" end="2:38.430">た</span><span begin="2:38.510" end="2:39.420">し</span> <span begin="2:39.820" end="2:40.030">死</span><span begin="2:40.070" end="2:40.220">に</span><span begin="2:40.280" end="2:40.610">た</span><span begin="2:40.610" end="2:40.700">い</span><span begin="2:40.730" end="2:40.850">の</span><span begin="2:40.950" end="2:41.170">か</span><span begin="2:41.190" end="2:41.360">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我 是想死吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나 죽고 싶은 걸까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I wonder if I want to die</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi shinitai no ka na</span></p><p begin="2:41.600" end="2:44.150" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:41.600" end="2:41.760">ま</span><span begin="2:41.810" end="2:41.990">さ</span><span begin="2:42.080" end="2:42.640">か</span> <span begin="2:43.140" end="2:43.300">ま</span><span begin="2:43.350" end="2:43.530">さ</span><span begin="2:43.620" end="2:43.810">か</span><span begin="2:43.840" end="2:44.150">ね</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">怎么会 怎么会呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">설마 설마 아니겠지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">No way no way at all</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Masaka masaka ne</span></p><p begin="2:43.830" end="2:49.200" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:43.830" end="2:44.250">完</span><span begin="2:44.270" end="2:44.720">全</span><span begin="2:44.720" end="2:44.870">な</span><span begin="2:44.930" end="2:45.350">空</span><span begin="2:45.380" end="2:49.200">へ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">向着完美的天空</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">완전한 하늘로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">To the perfect sky</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kanzen na sora e</span></p><p begin="2:45.180" end="2:49.310" itunes:key="L43" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:45.180" end="2:45.370">き</span><span begin="2:45.420" end="2:45.590">み</span><span begin="2:45.640" end="2:45.810">が</span> <span begin="2:45.840" end="2:46.170">だ</span><span begin="2:46.170" end="2:46.280">ん</span><span begin="2:46.280" end="2:46.650">だ</span><span begin="2:46.650" end="2:46.750">ん</span><span begin="2:46.750" end="2:47.200">灰</span><span begin="2:47.200" end="2:47.390">に</span><span begin="2:47.430" end="2:47.690">な</span><span begin="2:47.690" end="2:47.870">っ</span><span begin="2:47.870" end="2:48.080">て</span><span begin="2:48.280" end="2:48.630">ゆ</span><span begin="2:48.720" end="2:48.890">く</span><span begin="2:48.960" end="2:49.170">の</span><span begin="2:49.170" end="2:49.310">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你渐渐化作灰烬的模样</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 갈수록 재가 되어가는 것을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">As you gradually turned into ash</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi ga dandan hai ni natte yuku no o</span></p><p begin="2:49.350" end="2:52.020" itunes:key="L44" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:49.350" end="2:49.630">そ</span><span begin="2:49.630" end="2:49.830">っ</span><span begin="2:49.830" end="2:50.030">と</span> <span begin="2:50.080" end="2:50.190">み</span><span begin="2:50.280" end="2:50.500">つ</span><span begin="2:50.520" end="2:50.890">め</span><span begin="2:50.990" end="2:51.690">て</span><span begin="2:51.690" end="2:51.790">い</span><span begin="2:51.870" end="2:52.020">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我静静地注视着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">가만히 바라보고 있었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I softly gazed at you</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sotto mitsumeteita</span></p><p begin="2:52.280" end="2:55.140" itunes:key="L45" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:52.280" end="2:52.460">き</span><span begin="2:52.530" end="2:52.690">み</span><span begin="2:52.730" end="2:52.910">が</span> <span begin="2:52.940" end="2:53.320">だ</span><span begin="2:53.320" end="2:53.410">ん</span><span begin="2:53.410" end="2:53.750">だ</span><span begin="2:53.750" end="2:53.830">ん</span><span begin="2:53.830" end="2:54.260">海</span><span begin="2:54.290" end="2:54.490">に</span><span begin="2:54.520" end="2:54.710">な</span><span begin="2:54.710" end="2:54.970">っ</span><span begin="2:54.970" end="2:55.140">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你渐渐化作大海</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 갈수록 바다가 되어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">You gradually become the sea</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi ga dandan umi ni natte</span></p><p begin="2:55.390" end="2:56.870" itunes:key="L46" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:55.390" end="2:55.600">き</span><span begin="2:55.630" end="2:55.810">ら</span><span begin="2:55.860" end="2:56.070">め</span><span begin="2:56.070" end="2:56.210">い</span><span begin="2:56.300" end="2:56.500">て</span><span begin="2:56.520" end="2:56.870">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">闪烁着光芒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">반짝이고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Sparkling</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kirameiteru</span></p><p begin="2:57.180" end="2:58.530" itunes:key="L47" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:57.180" end="2:57.590">星</span><span begin="2:57.610" end="2:57.780">の</span><span begin="2:57.860" end="2:57.970">よ</span><span begin="2:57.970" end="2:58.060">う</span><span begin="2:58.080" end="2:58.530">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">宛如星辰</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">별처럼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Like a star</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hoshi no you ni</span></p><p begin="2:58.950" end="3:03.290" itunes:key="L48" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:58.950" end="2:59.390">あ</span><span begin="2:59.390" end="2:59.530">れ</span><span begin="2:59.620" end="2:59.800">か</span><span begin="2:59.830" end="3:00.020">ら</span><span begin="3:00.070" end="3:00.460">随</span><span begin="3:00.500" end="3:00.910">分</span><span begin="3:00.910" end="3:00.940">、</span><span begin="3:00.960" end="3:01.370">窓</span><span begin="3:01.400" end="3:01.520">の</span><span begin="3:01.580" end="3:02.230">外</span><span begin="3:02.300" end="3:02.440">も</span><span begin="3:02.520" end="3:02.880">変</span><span begin="3:02.950" end="3:03.150">わ</span><span begin="3:03.170" end="3:03.290">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">从那以后过了很久 窗外也变了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 후로 꽤나, 창밖도 변하고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Since then the view outside the window has changed quite a bit</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Are kara zuibun, mado no soto mo kawari</span></p><p begin="3:03.350" end="3:06.240" itunes:key="L49" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:03.350" end="3:03.520">つ</span><span begin="3:03.620" end="3:03.830">ま</span><span begin="3:03.850" end="3:04.030">ら</span><span begin="3:04.080" end="3:04.260">な</span><span begin="3:04.260" end="3:04.500">い</span><span begin="3:04.500" end="3:04.910">嘘</span><span begin="3:04.930" end="3:04.970">じ</span><span begin="3:04.970" end="3:05.130">ゃ</span><span begin="3:05.170" end="3:05.320">泣</span><span begin="3:05.380" end="3:05.580">け</span><span begin="3:05.620" end="3:05.770">な</span><span begin="3:05.860" end="3:05.990">く</span><span begin="3:06.070" end="3:06.240">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无聊的谎言已无法让我落泪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">시시한 거짓말로는 울 수 없어서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I can&apos;t cry over boring lies</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsumaranai uso ja nakenakute</span></p><p begin="3:06.530" end="3:11.200" itunes:key="L50" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:06.530" end="3:06.940">太</span><span begin="3:06.940" end="3:07.390">陽</span><span begin="3:07.630" end="3:07.850">に</span><span begin="3:08.080" end="3:08.260">手</span><span begin="3:08.290" end="3:08.470">を</span><span begin="3:08.510" end="3:08.670">伸</span><span begin="3:08.750" end="3:09.000">ば</span><span begin="3:09.020" end="3:09.130">し</span><span begin="3:09.180" end="3:09.590">て</span><span begin="3:09.660" end="3:09.970">み</span><span begin="3:10.070" end="3:10.200">た</span><span begin="3:10.310" end="3:10.480">け</span><span begin="3:10.500" end="3:10.660">れ</span><span begin="3:10.720" end="3:11.200">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">虽然试着向太阳伸出手</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">태양을 향해 손을 뻗어 보았지만</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I tried reaching my hand out to the sun but</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Taiyou ni te o nobashite mita keredo</span></p><p begin="3:11.610" end="3:13.160" itunes:key="L51" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:11.610" end="3:11.820">だ</span><span begin="3:11.860" end="3:12.010">め</span><span begin="3:12.080" end="3:12.200">み</span><span begin="3:12.310" end="3:13.060">た</span><span begin="3:13.060" end="3:13.160">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">似乎不行呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">안 될 것 같아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It seems hopeless</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dame mitai</span></p><p begin="3:13.580" end="3:17.820" itunes:key="L52" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:13.580" end="3:14.030">花</span><span begin="3:14.070" end="3:14.240">び</span><span begin="3:14.280" end="3:14.520">ら</span><span begin="3:14.720" end="3:14.940">が</span><span begin="3:15.180" end="3:15.600">前</span><span begin="3:15.620" end="3:16.270">髪</span><span begin="3:16.300" end="3:16.520">の</span><span begin="3:16.520" end="3:16.930">上</span><span begin="3:16.960" end="3:17.170">に</span><span begin="3:17.170" end="3:17.330">落</span><span begin="3:17.380" end="3:17.520">ち</span><span begin="3:17.610" end="3:17.820">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">花瓣落在刘海上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">꽃잎이 앞머리 위로 떨어져</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A petal fell on my bangs</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hanabira ga maegami no ue ni ochite</span></p><p begin="3:17.820" end="3:18.150" itunes:key="L53" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:17.820" end="3:18.060">う</span><span begin="3:18.060" end="3:18.150">ん</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">嗯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">응</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Yeah</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Un</span></p><p begin="3:18.680" end="3:24.850" itunes:key="L54" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:18.680" end="3:18.900">そ</span><span begin="3:18.950" end="3:19.120">れ</span><span begin="3:19.150" end="3:19.320">だ</span><span begin="3:19.400" end="3:24.850">け</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">仅此而已</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그것뿐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That&apos;s all</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore dake</span></p></div></body></tt>